# tdns-cli selects NO real algorithm implementations.
# It is a query/management tool, not a signer or validator: it only needs
# the name<->codepoint<->role metadata (compiled in for ALL registry
# algorithms via the generated metadata_algs.go) for CLI argument
# validation. Leaving this list empty keeps the binary pure-Go — no CIRCL,
# no liboqs/sqisign/qruov, no cgo.
